Look upon Korah, Dathan, and Abiram, they murmured againſt Moſes and Aaron, Prince, and Prieſt; and they ſuddenly went downe alive into the pit of hell. Num. 16.33.Tertul. 
               Hoc vero erat futuri judicij praejudicium;

 this doome is a fore-runner of the day of Doome, and a true Preſident of that ſentence, which ſhall paſſe upon diſobedient perſons in that dreadfull day: that ſo all thoſe, that read it, or heare it read, may take warning by their example, and avoyd the wrath to come.
